gameRecap.title: Game Recap: Grizzlies 108, Raptors 100
gameRecap.excerpt: The Grizzlies defeated the Raptors, 108-100. Jaren Jackson Jr. recorded 27 points, six steals, and five assists for the Grizzlies, with Luke Kennard adding 19 points and seven assists in the victory. RJ Barrett tallied 29 points and nine rebounds for the Raptors in the losing effort. The Grizzlies improve to 16-27, while the Raptors fall to 16-28.
